cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with the impact of multipath reflections on indoor visible light positioning systems, which involves the study of channel impulse response and received signal strength information. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper also involves image processing and computer vision techniques (cs.CV), machine learning algorithms (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with the use of LED bulbs and photodiodes for indoor positioning.
